引发的银行业风险顾虑开始蔓延到商品市场，国际原油价格盘中一度暴跌 8%，WTI 原油期货收盘暴跌 5.22% 报 67.61 美元 / 桶，NYMEX 天然气期货收跌 5.21%。 极端悲观的经济学家、有「末日博士」之称的努里尔·鲁比尼认为，瑞信可能「太大而不能救」，不排除倒闭风险，「瑞士信贷是欧洲和全球市场的雷曼时刻」。 瑞士信贷作为全球金融市场的重要参与者，是仅次于瑞银集团的瑞士第二大银行，截至 2022 年底其资产约为 5800 亿美元，是上周倒闭的硅谷银行规模的两倍多。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-52442054be1ba1005244f2ecec2ea28b_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/589909006"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+tyYhP3qgJoCEAMaCDkzMzcyNDMzINiVyqAGMA84+AhAInIJNTg5OTA5MDA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1679186794.829576", "card_id": "Q_587697746", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 182}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "工作三年，发现做的工作不是自己想要的，转行还来得及吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/587697746"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+tyYhP3qgJoCEAMaCDkyODgxMTM3IKbDkKAGMAE4mgJAI3IJNTg3Njk3NzQ2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1679186794.8299563", "card_id": "Q_500406718", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 885}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "编程那么难，为什么不弄一个大众一学就会的计算机语言呢?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "就像链接蓝牙那样，一看就会的，一做就懂的那种。 相当于一种模板，你往里面装东西就行的那种。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-2c63cc5bfd4c1b6187bf2b357258071a_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/500406718"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+tyYhP3qgJoCEAMaCDcz